name: New Year's Memorabilia Box
description:
New Year's Memorabilia Box, now available!

Get Charms and Wish Plaques with character and group motifs as New Year's exclusive Memorabilia items from the New Year's Memorabilia Box.

Charms and Wish Plaques are Limited Time Memorabilia items.
You can display acquired Charms and Wish Plaques on your Custom Profile.
notice:
•Free Crystals will be used first.
•Duplicate Memorabilia may be pulled from the Memorabilia Box. In that case, you will be able to use the duplicate item in your Custom Profile more than once.
•Memorabilia are pulled one at a time based on existing drop rates. The drop rates therefore do not mean that, for example, Memorabilia with a drop rate of 1% are guaranteed to appear once every 100 pulls.
•Drop rates can be viewed from the drop rates tab.
The drop rates that are displayed on the drop rates tab are rounded to the fourth decimal place, so the total may not exactly add up to 100%.
•After starting the Memorabilia Box, even if the app should force-quit or be disconnected without displaying the results screen, pulled Memorabilia will be saved and viewable from Memorabilia in Custom Profile.
•The Limited Time Memorabilia from this Memorabilia Box may be made available again in the future. Any potential future availability is currently TBD.
•The Memorabilia Box schedule is subject to change without notice.
